CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 22, 1945. pg. 13, reads: "BACKDROP - The famed Cathedral of Learning at the University of Pittsburgh provides a suitable backdrop for the charms of Margery T. Johnson of Hermitage Street, as she poses for the Courier camera man. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Marjorie T. Johnston wearing dark dress, seated on edge of Schenley fountain with University of Pittsburgh's Cathedral of Learning in background, Oakland
